19:16.320 --> 19:18.728
A little bit of military strategy.

19:20.449 --> 19:22.572
Sounds like the jazz to me.

19:35.089 --> 19:36.797
[Phone rings]

19:38.634 --> 19:40.543
JAlME: Mr. Gaines, this is Jaime CoIIins.

